There is a Select class, on that class pass the dropdown element.
Ex : country = Select(driver.find_element(By.XPATH, "//select[@id='input-country']"))

country.select_by_visible_text("India") # Preferable
country.select_by_value("4") 
country.select_by_index(13)

options will return all the option under the button/select/* classs as a web element.


1) select option from dropdown

2) Select option from dropdown without using built-in function

3) Actions without using Select class



Boostrap - Dropdown elements without select class is said to be Boostrap.
